<div id="pf1dd9" class="pf w33 h127" data-page-no="1dd9"><div class="pc pc1dd9 w33 h127"><div class="t ma32 xbd he y875 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">man should be the ruler of his own house. With an understanding of Eastern </div><div class="t m581 xbd he y15f2 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">customs, then and now, it is difficult to believe that this condition did not </div><div class="t m9b3 xbd he y6f8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">obtain in Persian households. The decree of the king was the outgrowth of </div><div class="t m574 xbd he y4a3 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">his drunken rage and the masculine self-esteem, as well as the evident reaction&apos; </div><div class="t m162 xbd he y718 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of his accusing conscience against which he rebelled. With a group of </div><div class="t m267 xbd he yf76 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">councilors, equally under the influence of a long indulged appetite for wine, </div><div class="t mb91 xbd he y6c9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">little better judgment was to be expected. </div><div class="t mac3 x6c h1 ye05 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson 6 for August 6, 1938 </div><div class="t m5cc x5f h25 y767 ff4 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY LESSON STUDY: </div><div class="t m9fa x6a h2f y927 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Place a check mark in the proper space. </div><div class="t m22f3 x11 h2f y29b ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUNDAY I </div><div class="t mb94 x83 h25 y6ce ff4 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MONDAY </div><div class="t m3937 x1 h2f yfb9 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I </div><div class="t m5d5 x30 h25 yfe9 ff4 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">TUESDAY </div><div class="t m3937 x1d h2f yfe9 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I </div><div class="t m1d8 x77 h25 y53 ff4 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WEDNESDAY THURSDAY </div><div class="t m3937 xa8 h2f y8ee ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I  </div><div class="t m629 xbf h25 y53 ff4 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FRIDAY </div><div class="t mbf1 x7f h6 y53 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I </div><div class="t m2fd x94 h25 y53 ff4 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SABBATH </div><